\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Architecture & Key Innovation\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Architecture
\f1\b0 : Transformer based on 
\f0\b LTG-BERT
\f1\b0  with attention-gating and 
\f0\b Adaptive Layer Normalization (AdaLN)
\f1\b0  modulation for timestep injection[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Training Objective
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b Masked Diffusion Language Modeling (MDLM)
\f1\b0  \'97 applies diffusion training objectives to language modeling under strict data constraints[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Key Innovation
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b Frequency-informed masking
\f1\b0  \'97 masking probabilities are biased toward 
\f5\i rare tokens
\f1\i0 , ensuring the model learns more from low-frequency vocabulary while maintaining theoretical validity under the Negative Evidence Lower Bound (NELBO) objective[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Noise Schedule
\f1\b0 : Cosine masking schedule (chosen for submission); also explored two-mode schedules and various noise weighting schemes[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Model Size
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b 126.6M parameters
\f1\b0 [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Vocabulary
\f1\b0 : 16,384 tokens (BPE)[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Sequence Length
\f1\b0 : 512[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Batch Size
\f1\b0 : 512[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Training Duration
\f1\b0 : 10 epochs on the 100M-word BabyLM strict corpus[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.05056v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls1\ilvl0
