\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Why It Stands Out\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 MTP Forward Curriculum is the first demonstration that 
\f0\b MTP training benefits carry over to sub-130M models
\f1\b0  under data constraints. The curriculum design avoids the "training bias" that hurts static MTP in early training phases. Gains are especially large on WUG morphological tasks.[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://aclanthology.org/2025.babylm-main.41/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 aclanthology}}]\
