\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Training Objective
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b Adaptive Masked Language Modeling (AMLM)
\f1\b0  \'97 dynamically adjusts the probability of masking individual tokens based on the model's 
\f5\i current ability to predict them
\f1\i0  (hard metric = accuracy-based; soft metric = loss-based)[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2510.20475v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
