\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Hard AMLM
\f1\b0 : Tokens the model already predicts correctly are masked with lower probability 
\f6 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  focus training on harder tokens\
\ls4\ilvl1
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Decaying mask
\f1\b0 : Starts at 40% masking, linearly decays to 15% over training\
\ls4\ilvl1
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
