\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 AMLM directly addresses the inefficiency in uniform MLM masking, ensuring 
\f0\b training budget is spent on tokens the model hasn't yet learned
\f1\b0 . The sub-token embedding extension is a significant orthogonal contribution to morphological task performance.[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/html/2510.20475v1"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 arxiv}}]\
