\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Architecture
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b GPT-BERT
\f1\b0  (Charpentier & Samuel 2024) \'97 hybrid encoder-decoder architecture capable of both causal and masked inference[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://aclanthology.org/2025.babylm-main.34/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 aclanthology}}]\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Training Objective
\f1\b0 : 
\f0\b Active Curriculum Language Modeling (ACLM)
\f1\b0  \'97 surprisal-based example selection to construct a training curriculum. Examples are ordered by a model's surprisal score; harder/more surprising examples are seen later in training[{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://aclanthology.org/2025.babylm-main.34/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 aclanthology}}]\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Key Innovations
\f1\b0 :\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Surprisal-based 
\f0\b active selection
\f1\b0  of training examples (not random ordering)\
\ls5\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Targeted 
\f0\b hyperparameter search
\f1\b0  over tokenizer size (4k, 6k vocab) and batch size\
